snippet.title: Galactic Civilizations IV: Supernova - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
www.galciv4.com/supernova

Your choices for dominion are endless: Planetary Conquest, Cultural Domination, Political Alliances, Technological Supremacy.  

In Galactic Civilizations, you are the leader of a space-faring civilization at the dawn of the 24th century. Your mission is to spread your civilization across the known universe. 

Make the galaxy yours!

#pcgaming #strategygames #trailer
